---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <h1>The Tóki Flow</h1>
    <p>
      Every packaging journey is unique. That’s why we’ve shaped our process into five flexible phases - designed to meet you exactly where you are. <br />
      Explore each step below to see which one suits your needs best. You can choose one phase or follow the full flow - whichever fits your needs best.
    </p>
    <div class="line"></div>
    <h2>The Five Phases</h2>
    <Flow />
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  h1 {
    color: #3a544a;
  }
  h2 {
    color: #311407;
  }
  .line {
    height: 2px; /* Tykkelse */
    background-color: #3a544a; /* grøne linje */
    width: 100%; /* Fuldbredde */
    margin: 20px 0; /* Lidt afstand */
  }
</style>
